  95. ‌let allocated_bytes () =
  96.   let (mi, pro, ma) = counters () in
  97.   (mi +. ma -. pro) *. float_of_int (Sys.word_size / 8)

  106. ‌type alarm = bool Atomic.t

  109. ‌let rec call_alarm arec =
  110.   if Atomic.get arec.active then begin
  111.     let finally () = finalise call_alarm arec in
  112.     Fun.protect ~finally arec.f
  113.   end


  116. let create_alarm f =
  117.   let arec = { active = Atomic.make true; f = f } in
  118.   finalise call_alarm arec;
  119.   arec.active
